peardb - a key value server

Usage:
  peardb [--daemonize | -a DB_PATH | -p PORT | -w WORKERS | -b NANOS | -s MEGAS]
  peardb stat
  peardb --help

Options:
  -d --daemonize           Run as a daemon.
  -a --path DB_PATH        Path where database files will be kept [default: store]
  -p --port PORT           Port to listen on [default: 8888]
  -w --workers WORKERS     Number of worker threads [default: 8]
  -b --batch_period NANOS  Number of nano seconds between batch commits [default: 50000]
  -s --db_size MEGAS       Size of database in megabytes [default: 1000]
  -h --help                Prints a short usage summary.
